OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FStaying mostly cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Frain turning more showery and a few
OL,9,Fclearer spells developing between
OL,10,Fshowers in the east. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with a few
OL,13,Fbright spells and frequent showers
OL,14,Ffeeding in from the west. Showers
OL,15,Fheavy at times and forming longer
OL,16,Fspells of rain later. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
